    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superb mechanical example of the peak analog driving era. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving valvetrain that remains crisp and responsive. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throws, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery out of corners. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis retains its signature balance with refreshed bushings and a taut suspension setup. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and structural integrity are excellent, making this a turn-key performance machine for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
