    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly captures the essence of a reliable, high-quality driver. The exterior retains a beautiful, deep luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014typical signs of a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the leather upholstery is clean and firm, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All interior electronics, including the dual-zone climate control, heated seats, and the updated infotainment system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, benefiting from a documented history of on-time oil changes and a recent multi-point inspection. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide a confident, firm response. This car offers a seamless blend of performance and sophistication, ready for its next chapter with a buyer who appreciates a vehicle that has been treated with care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
